room_title: Escape room "The Agency" by Escape the Room Philly in Philadelphia
review: Excellent experience. The Agency was fun and challenging. Can't wait to check out some of the other rooms that ERP has in the future.

room_title: Escape room "The Agency" by Escape the Room Philly in Philadelphia
review: The Agency was so dope! We really had a good time it was myself and 6 other friends! We escaped with 7 mins to spare. Dexter was super cool. Very fun, worth the money, and not easy at all...critical thinking is a must!

room_title: Escape room "The Agency" by Escape the Room Philly in Philadelphia
review: We did this last night and it was so much fun! We got so close with the key in our hand but ran out of time! I absolutely recommend doing this it was so much fun and much harder then you even anticipated!

room_title: Escape room "The Agency" by Escape the Room Philly in Philadelphia
review: We went for my sister's birthday last night. We had two teams of 7 that got to go head to head. One team won with ten minutes to spare and the other came close but lost. Can't wait to come back for a rematch on the dig! Puzzles were fun to solve and was great for teamwork!
